document_data.History:
In the 14{{th}} century [[DR]], several normal werewolverines were transformed into [[blacktooth]] dire werewolverines by the use of [[blacktooth paste]].

{{Quote 
|The [[Spellguard]] tells me that in their hybrid forms they were much larger than normal werewolverines, and I think I may have discovered why—blacktooth paste.
|[[Taern Hornblade]]
}}

During this time, the park in the [[Hunter's District]] of [[Silverymoon]] was terrorized by a trio of [[blacktooth]] dire werewolverines loyal to [[anth-Malar]], a [[Chosen]] of [[Malar]]. Those of Silverymoon requested aid, and a group of [[dwarves]] intended to help those in need. However, [[Duallan Tiergar]], a dwarf [[wizard]], was bitten on the way and turned into a blacktooth dire werewolverine himself.
